               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430508-name-1136" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430508-name-1136" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430508-name-1136" type="surname" value="APTED"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430508-name-1136" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE APTED</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a baker, and live in Lisson-street, Marylebone. On the 30th of April I went to Steven-street—I was drunk, laid on the floor, and went to sleep—I heard a whispering—I had a sovereign on the table—the prisoner came in, took it, and said that was what he wanted, and ran out—I followed him, and stumbled—I called the police—I found him in a brothel in Great James-street, Lisson-grove in about ten minutes—I asked him to give me the sovereign—he said he had not got it, if I would go back he would give it me, or make it all right.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
